description:
here's my first upload to the tezos blockchain, it's called PLASMA and it is the instrumental to an interlude that i created. if you purchase, you're allowed to use the beat for non-profit purposes and upload the work with credit to me (for example, putting in the title [Prod. by REM)

your support means a lot to me and i hope yall enjoy the sounds. you can find me on all socials as @rem_cycles
